definition: hundred knots of worry in one's intestines (idiom); weighed down with anxiety
(of a plant) to produce (fruit or seeds)/Taiwan pr. [jie2]
knot/sturdy/bond/to tie/to bind/to check out (of a hotel)

sentences.english: Don't worry about your lipstick or your height, because it's not going to matter.
sentences.chinese: 別爲你的脣膏或身高而愁腸百結，因爲這並不緊要。

sentences.english: To have money is a fear, not to have it grief.
sentences.chinese: 有錢擔驚受怕，無錢愁腸百結。
